1. OCSPD

1) remove "ldap_ca_1" and "dbms_ldap" sections from /etc/ocspd/ocspd.conf as  we do not use LDAP,
   remove HSM section as we do not use hardware key management (LunaCA3, LunaSA)

2) add MIME type to /etc/nginx/mime.types:

application/x-pkcs7-crl               crl;

3) added config for crl.gamehack.com:

server {
    listen       80;
    server_name  crl.gamehack.com;
    root         /var/www/html;
    
    location / {
        deny all;
    }

    location /crls/ghssl.crl {
        expires 2d;
    }
}

4) add config for OCSP daemon
server {
    listen       80;
    server_name  ocsp.gamehack.com;

    location / {
        proxy_pass http://localhost:2560/;
    }

    error_log /var/log/nginx/ca.gamehack.com.error_log error;
    access_log /var/log/nginx/ca.gamehack.com.access_log main;
}

5) add subconfig to default virtual host:

set $ocsp  1;
if ( $request_method != POST ) {
    set $ocsp 0;
}
if ( $content_type !~* "application/ocsp-request" ) {
    set $ocsp 0;
}
if ($ocsp) {
    rewrite ^ /ocsp break;
}
location = /ocsp {
    proxy_pass http://localhost:2560;
}

6) Add our CA certificate to trusted store:
cp -a /etc/ssl/certs/f5e6bac4.pem /etc/pki/ca-trust/source/anchors/
cat /etc/ssl/certs/f5e6bac4.pem  >> /etc/pki/tls/cert.pem
update-ca-trust
c_rehash